{"tid":2464132,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"環球時報依家講既加速主義，其實就同五毛係連登日日鬥黃的原理一樣","createTime":"2021-03-27T08:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:39:49.000Z","uid":171506,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73bbae97ccd682b44c45e271601bbf1c195991a6","tid":2464132,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"當然，支持新疆綿花唔會真係有人加速，係官方搵個理由縮沙啫<br />\n<br />\n不過，將「自己人」的門檻推到天咁高，然後屌番「自己人」無撚用，無論鬥黃也好，加速也好，<br />\n呢招玩得純熟，真係好難破解<br />\n加速主義呢個名詞好似來自品葱，大陸人真係玩政治高手。"},{"pid":"c348c560a04496f23c5e27527df27980125c3d1b","tid":2464132,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1647bd7d4940242d41d316671b0fa1bcf525cc35","tid":2464132,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbbKSWeZdGVwcDKfnodA8wLG5Esvh3qkneSMUexk4g2p8?filename=Br2XKc6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBr2XKc6.gif&h=3c6a4035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3c092a2f9638b47c59ac54bcb772791d430e601","tid":2464132,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"佢哋網絡論壇微博<br />\n意見已經咁單一 咁一言堂<br />\n尚且都可以有咁多人 加速到 分化到 鬥到紅<br />\n(當然有啲真心膠 有啲牆內反賊玩嘢既 睇品葱都知)<br />\n睇連登既<br />\n真係自己清醒 睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4068907b4267f98aac3469680f89219efc19513c","tid":2464132,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"每次上連登都要block幾條友，佢地可以不斷有新ac"},{"pid":"c8d51ca85a212e918f94bba09ebc082e2f614554","tid":2464132,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"連登衰極最尾都係會有人好似樓主咁出黎屌<br />\n大陸唔會有，所以可以加速到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c5c13110ce5e97a8102649827bf92bfd3fc2ea","tid":2464132,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8d51ca85a212e918f94bba09ebc082e2f614554","tid":2464132,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"連登衰極最尾都係會有人好似樓主咁出黎屌<br />\n大陸唔會有，所以可以加速到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"好似清朝後期一樣"},{"pid":"db8edf6a7664e02f948c461bbe20b4d13d73d45b","tid":2464132,"uid":171506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c8d51ca85a212e918f94bba09ebc082e2f614554","tid":2464132,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"連登衰極最尾都係會有人好似樓主咁出黎屌<br />\n大陸唔會有，所以可以加速到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"大陸禁制言論自由，以為有助維穩，但其實係會加速到失控。"},{"pid":"0c0354a478b8259c951dea499cc8444080dca533","tid":2464132,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"多角度思維係自由思想必需<br />\n唔係傻西假膠會明呢啲真正意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f904a4f5eab4cc1a49183ab559b0a0c4be332002","tid":2464132,"uid":128261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"一早應該加速主義<br />\n以前溫影帝支那，扮豬食老虎嘅年代，就係支那發展得最快，最呃到人嘅年代<br />\n當年連高登仔都「我係中國人呀hi」<br />\n鬼佬就更加唔係講"},{"pid":"a33bba3ae14fb0c572fe2cf8ac6a95930a2bde9b","tid":2464132,"uid":59037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9602e1c97c4c6eaa42144215559ddf727e89babd","tid":2464132,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"黃藍店宣傳，增加藍店生意興隆機會<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTYBcSsAe9Y1Hk5BdBxogNcfKgMjw3fwwo4zQMZ4DGmnf?filename=ACxgZYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACxgZYH.png&h=25c41b61&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n迫政府封MPF逃生門<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPBEc1iuov1W2mkMSi7GRVKyiUcAh7seWXMSMkfWFZZcy?filename=CYBNmZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYBNmZV.jpg&h=ee33fe84&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n踢爆食客亂寫紙仔，幫強制安心出行鋪路<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVSToxEMDM47fwyhQSVUxZN76MeTSafHDxrUCcoDxezV4?filename=HXZK8E2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXZK8E2.png&h=02a64d5f&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殖入式洗腦 向讀者灌輸「每個人都應該要害怕病毒」既意識形態<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmakf8PxkTc61tKKPLNKizEEAxXcqvmHJY6DhgubxdKWfv?filename=NvnkGZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvnkGZY.png&h=dbf52c58&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫警察漂白<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZCyXoATfBRYcJPWnpm36omPAxsyk2mv19Jxs6GAiMnij?filename=2NhMCyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NhMCyf.jpg&h=54e687d5&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n <br />\n上面都係呢一個月發生，都仲未計上年理大香港人滅團單野<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vi7kxOS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVi7kxOS.jpg&h=2f49d72d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkqKe2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkqKe2b.jpg&h=0d2f5701&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvGaaAt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvGaaAt.jpg&h=52f5a461&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRzJp2B2tnmvge7fZiswjrWFqCd1vaNFY8gDqMYsMPpPt?filename=o0fREtO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0fREtO.jpg&h=4a524159&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWBXWk7QVqU5SZPQZAiee1FFZPeFwqQWjJdaZohGSA1jr?filename=75QqJVx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75QqJVx.jpg&h=eee4ba70&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcJjdkZTndt4ssqHefmifX6viPraPoKb7hYxzk91E1xEu?filename=uWB11Hb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWB11Hb.jpg&h=0a820ab5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GPQeCfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGPQeCfw.jpg&h=027c2e85&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nhDscOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhDscOR.jpg&h=3e555821&s={SIZE}\" />  </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上既野泛民完全無叫過大家去做，去保持熱度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NWmhfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NWmhfv.jpg&h=0cb8e5db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n而家仲要灌輸放棄抗爭意識，全部抗爭都係送頭無撚用，已經無空間，應該乜都唔好做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緬甸人一直係諗點贏<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRLna5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRLna5H.jpg&h=93002bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ki0ROSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKi0ROSo.png&h=b69a6104&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而泛民就係賣慘情，再賣恐懼、最後賣假希望，叫大家一係等救世主一係移民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係叫你地唔好再做呢啲仆街野消磿港人抗爭意志幫政權維穩<br />\n原來咁樣就係叫對泛民要求高？"},{"pid":"a2da7ce1372a40d6b844eea1fcfe339394fb7668","tid":2464132,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a33bba3ae14fb0c572fe2cf8ac6a95930a2bde9b","tid":2464132,"uid":59037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d62a022ae685d23efd55232ad30e591781c966c9","tid":2464132,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f904a4f5eab4cc1a49183ab559b0a0c4be332002","tid":2464132,"uid":128261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"一早應該加速主義<br />\n以前溫影帝支那，扮豬食老虎嘅年代，就係支那發展得最快，最呃到人嘅年代<br />\n當年連高登仔都「我係中國人呀hi」<br />\n鬼佬就更加唔係講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"時勢改變咗"},{"pid":"53b49d7a6514aacfd277a764be7cb4367195d4e5","tid":2464132,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"不如諗下邊撚個係總加速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}